{"id":542551,"date":[{"year":1975,"month":3,"day":2}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"78","ytitle":"","mtitle":"扎根山区心更红","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山茶林场四连"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山巅挺立万年松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨涤青松傲苍穹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的儿女听党话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春战歌向党颂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立志务农志不移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎根山区心更红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘洒满腔青春血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安排山河立新功。"}]}